== 起因==
想要实现 google 和 twitter 的 Oauth2, 但是目前用的主机又是国内的阿里云, 没法实现了.

好在手头还有1台国外的 vps, 于是想在这台 vps 上搭建 https 的反向代理, 实现 Oauth2
## ssl证书
ningx 要反向代理是需要 ssl 证书的,
```bash
openssl genrsa -out server.key 1024
openssl req -new -key server.key -out server.csr
openssl x509 -req -days 365 -in server.csr -signkey server.key -out server.crt
```
## nginx 配置
```
    server {
        listen       443;
        server_name  api.twitter.bigzhu.org;
        ssl on;
        ssl_certificate /home/bigzhu/Dropbox/bigzhu.org/server.crt;
        ssl_certificate_key /home/bigzhu/Dropbox/bigzhu.org/server.key;
        ssl_protocols SSLv3 TLSv1;
        ssl_ciphers ALL:-ADH:+HIGH:+MEDIUM:-LOW:-SSLv2:-EXP;
	    location / {
          proxy_redirect off;
          proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
          proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
          proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto https;
          proxy_pass https://api.twitter.com;
  	    }
