## 前言
对象持久化.回忆下[d3js bar 2 读书笔记](d3js bar 2 读书笔记.md),写那一篇的时候我还没看 object constancy

那时在`绑定复杂数据类型`那一节,其实已经尝试做了对象持久化了.貌似有些做法不对,瞎折腾来着的.
## key
data 方法在绑定 object 的时候,可以指定key,用于后续的过滤.

```js
function key(d) {
  return d.State;
}
var bar = svg.selectAll(".bar")
    .data(top, function(d) { return d.State; });
```
如此一来,d3才能准确的取到 bar.enter() , bar.exit() 以及匹配的.

http://bost.ocks.org/mike/bar/2/

## 比例尺换算
常常会出现需要换算比例尺的情况.

比如 bar chart

要根据给定的值来按比例设定 chart 的长度

```js
var data = [4, 8, 15, 16, 23, 42];

var width = 420,
    barHeight = 20;

var x = d3.scale.linear()
    .domain([0, d3.max(data)])
    .range([0, width]);

var chart = d3.select(".chart")
    .attr("width", width)
    .attr("height", barHeight * data.length);

var bar = chart.selectAll("g")
    .data(data)
  .enter().append("g")
    .attr("transform", function(d, i) { return "translate(0," + i * barHeight + ")"; });

bar.append("rect")
    .attr("width", x)
    .attr("height", barHeight - 1);
......
```
其中
```js
var x = d3.scale.linear()
    .domain([0, d3.max(data)])
    .range([0, width]);
```
x 就是建立的换算比例尺的函数.

先只管用就行了,不用去管具体的实现细节
```js
var x = d3.scale.linear()
    .domain([0, 100])
    .range([0, 10]);
console.log(x(99));
```
会返回 9.9
## 绑定复杂数据类型
ps:参看[d3js Object Constancy 读书笔记](d3js Object Constancy 读书笔记.md),这里的有些做法可能不对.

一直以来的例子,都是绑定最简单的数字类型的 array
```js
var data = [4, 8, 15, 16, 23, 42];
```
实际应用中哪有那么简单.

d3 的链式编程决定了,只能拿 array 来绑定,类似 backbone 的 collection.
```js
var data = [ {"name": "john", "age": 13},
        {"name": "matt", "age":14}
];
```
下面我们来对这个例子改造,同时显示姓名和年纪
```js
var data = [4, 8, 15, 16, 23, 42];

var width = 420,
    barHeight = 20;

var x = d3.scale.linear()
    .domain([0, d3.max(data)])
    .range([0, width]);

var chart = d3.select(".chart")
    .attr("width", width)
    .attr("height", barHeight * data.length);

var bar = chart.selectAll("g")
    .data(data)
  .enter().append("g")
    .attr("transform", function(d, i) { return "translate(0," + i * barHeight + ")"; });

bar.append("rect")
    .attr("width", x)
    .attr("height", barHeight - 1);

bar.append("text")
    .attr("x", function(d) { return x(d) - 3; })
    .attr("y", barHeight / 2)
    .attr("dy", ".3em")
    .text(function(d) { return d; });
```
参看 [js 对复杂 json 取 max](js 对复杂 json 取 max.md)

改了以后变成这样,实现再 bar 头显示名字
```js
var data = [
{"name": "john", "age": 13},
{"name": "matt", "age":14},
{"name": "bigzhu", "age":30},
];

var width = 420,
    barHeight = 20;

var x = d3.scale.linear()
.domain([0, d3.max(data, function(d){return d.age})])
.range([0, width]);

var chart = d3.select(".chart")
.attr("width", width)
.attr("height", barHeight * data.length);

var bar = chart.selectAll("g")
.data(data)
.enter().append("g")
.attr("transform", function(d, i) { return "translate(0," + i * barHeight + ")"; });

bar.append("rect")
.attr("width", function(d){return x(d.age);})
.attr("height", barHeight - 1);

bar.append("text")
.attr("x", function(d) { return x(d.age)-3; })
.attr("y", barHeight / 2)
.attr("dy", ".3em")
.text(function(d) { return d.age; });

bar.append("text")
.attr("style", 'text-anchor: start;font-size:12px')
.attr("x", function(d) {return x(0)+3; })
.attr("y", barHeight / 2)
.attr("dy", ".3em")
.text(function(d) { return d.name; });
```

虽然叫数据绑定,但是仅仅是数据发生了变化,并不会让d3操作的dom发生变化,还是得自己来操作.

比如如下的脚本,看着就清楚了

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>

text {
  font: bold 48px monospace;
}

.enter {
  fill: green;
}

.update {
  fill: #333;
}

</style>
<body>
<script src="http://d3js.org/d3.v2.min.js?2.10.1"></script>
<script>

var alphabet = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz".split("");

var width = 960,
    height = 500;

var svg = d3.select("body").append("svg")
    .attr("width", width)
    .attr("height", height)
  .append("g")
    .attr("transform", "translate(32," + (height / 2) + ")");

function update(data) {

  // DATA JOIN
  // Join new data with old elements, if any.
  var text = svg.selectAll("text")
      .data(data);

  // UPDATE
  // Update old elements as needed.
  text.attr("class", "update");

  // ENTER
  // Create new elements as needed.
  text.enter().append("text")
      .attr("class", "enter")
      .attr("x", function(d, i) { return i * 32; })
      .attr("dy", ".35em");

  // ENTER + UPDATE
  // Appending to the enter selection expands the update selection to include
  // entering elements; so, operations on the update selection after appending to
  // the enter selection will apply to both entering and updating nodes.
  text.text(function(d) { return d; });

  // EXIT
  // Remove old elements as needed.
  text.exit().remove();
}

// The initial display.
update(alphabet);

// Grab a random sample of letters from the alphabet, in alphabetical order.
setInterval(function() {
  update(shuffle(alphabet)
      .slice(0, Math.floor(Math.random() * 26))
      .sort());
}, 1500);

// Shuffles the input array.
function shuffle(array) {
  var m = array.length, t, i;
  while (m) {
    i = Math.floor(Math.random() * m--);
