报错
```bash
/usr/local/apache2/bin/apxs  -i -a -c -I /usr/local/pgsql/include -L /usr/local/pgsql/lib -lpq mod_auth_pgsql.c
make: /usr/local/apache2/bin/apxs: Command not found
make: *** ![pic](shared) Error 127
