<local:GameClass xmlns:local="*"  xmlns:mx="http://www.adobe.com/2006/mxml"  layout="absolute"  creationComplete="init()">

  <mx:Script>

  <![[CDATA[[

    import org.ActionScriptClass;

    internal function init():void{

        ActionScriptClass.setMxml(this);

    }

  ]]>

</mx:Script>        

<mx:Button id="btn"></mx:Button>

</local:GameClass>
```


